## Connecting multiple commands to a single event.

MyButton:

<MyButton@Button>:
	text: "Push Me, Baby"
	on_release: print("Give it to me, baby!")
	italic: True
	font_size: 60
	on_press: self.font_size = 100
	on_press: self.text = "You Pushed Me!"
	on_release: self.font_size = 60
	on_release: self.text = "Push Me, Baby"

